data.config:
[Global]
secret-name = "vsphere-creds"
secret-namespace = "kube-system"
insecure-flag = "1"

[VirtualCenter "vcdc.shbfinance.com.vn"]
port = "443"

datacenters = "SHB Finance DC"

[Workspace]
server = "vcdc.shbfinance.com.vn"
datacenter = "SHB Finance DC"
default-datastore = "/SHB Finance DC/datastore/FC24"
folder = "/SHB Finance DC/vm/ocp-prod01-fbnvt"
resourcepool-path = "/SHB Finance DC/host/HA-Cluster1//Resources"

annotations.kubernetes.io/description: The install-config content used to create the cluster.  The cluster configuration may have evolved since installation, so check cluster configuration resources directly if you are interested in the current cluster state.

data.install-config:
additionalTrustBundlePolicy: Proxyonly
apiVersion: v1
baseDomain: shbfinance.com.vn
compute:
- architecture: amd64
  hyperthreading: Enabled
  name: worker
  platform: {}
  replicas: 3
controlPlane:
  architecture: amd64
  hyperthreading: Enabled
  name: master
  platform: {}
  replicas: 3
metadata:
  creationTimestamp: null
  name: ocp-prod01
networking:
  clusterNetwork:
  - cidr: 10.128.0.0/14
    hostPrefix: 23
  machineNetwork:
  - cidr: 10.0.0.0/16
  networkType: OVNKubernetes
  serviceNetwork:
  - 172.30.0.0/16
platform:
  vsphere:
    apiVIPs:
    - 10.0.65.7
    failureDomains:
    - name: generated-failure-domain
      region: generated-region
      server: vcdc.shbfinance.com.vn
      topology:
        computeCluster: /SHB Finance DC/host/HA-Cluster1
        datacenter: SHB Finance DC
        datastore: /SHB Finance DC/datastore/FC24
        networks:
        - VLAN_65
        resourcePool: /SHB Finance DC/host/HA-Cluster1//Resources
      zone: generated-zone
    ingressVIPs:
    - 10.0.65.8
    vcenters:
    - datacenters:
      - SHB Finance DC
      password: ""
      server: vcdc.shbfinance.com.vn
      user: ""
publish: External
pullSecret: ""
sshKey: |
  ssh-rsa  ocp@dc-ocp-bastion
